  "prompt": "What should I do? How can I be happy?",
  "response": "Here are some suggestions for finding happiness:\n\n1. Personal well-being\n- Practice self-care\n- Exercise regularly\n- Get enough sleep\n- Eat a balanced diet\n- Manage stress through meditation or mindfulness\n\n2. Mental health\n- Cultivate positive thinking\n- Practice gratitude\n- Set realistic goals\n- Learn from challenges\n- Seek professional help if needed\n\n3. Relationships\n- Build and maintain meaningful connections\n- Communicate openly\n- Show empathy\n- Spend time with supportive people\n- Nurture close relationships\n\n4. Personal growth\n- Pursue your passions\n- Learn new skills\n- Challenge yourself\n- Read and stay curious\n- Set personal development goals\n\n5. Purpose and meaning\n- Define your values\n- Contribute to others\n- Volunteer\n- Find work that feels meaningful\n- Create personal goals\n\n6. Mindset\n- Practice acceptance\n- Let go of things you can't control\n- Be kind to yourself\n- Embrace imperfection\n- Focus on the present moment\n\nRemember, happiness is a journey, not a destination. It's different for everyone, so explore what works best for you.\n\nWould you like to discuss any of these areas in more depth?",
